<p>THANK</p>
<p>gratiam habere refers to the feeling of gratitude.</p>
<p>gratias habere ditto.</p>
<p>gratias agere refers to the speech act of thanking someone for a favour.</p>
<p>gratiam referre refers to the expression of one's gratitude through action.</p>
<p/>
<p>GRATEFUL</p>
<p>gratus refers to feelings of gratefulness.</p>
<p>memor refers to an awareness of a debt of gratitude.</p>
